<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Security Assessment | CyberMatch</title>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Consistent Site Header -->
    <header>
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img src="images/cybermatch-logo.png" alt="CyberMatch Logo" class="site-logo">
            <span class="logo-text">CyberMatch</span>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="assessment.html" class="active">Assessment</a></li>
                <li><a href="threat-index.html">Threat Index</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Asymmetric Main Container Layout: CSS Grid (3fr 1fr) -->
    <div class="sidebar-layout">
        
        <!-- Left Column: Main Interactive Quiz Content (3fr) -->
        <main class="main-content">
            <h1>Personalized Security Assessment</h1>
            <p>Answer these short, engaging questions about your technology footprint to help us build your customized security profile. We evaluate your physical devices, data handling sensitivity, and financial parameters.</p>
            
            <!-- Required Image 1: Progress-Tracking Infographic Wizard layout -->
            <div class="wizard-progress-container">
                <img src="images/progress-wizard.png" alt="Infographic progress tracking bar showing Step 1 of 3 completed" class="progress-img">
            </div>

            <!-- Mock Quiz Form Interface -->
            <form class="assessment-form" onsubmit="return false;">
                <fieldset>
                    <legend>Step 1: Your Digital Footprint</legend>
                    
                    <label for="device-type">What is your primary computing device?</label>
                    <select id="device-type" name="device-type">
                        <option value="windows">Windows PC / Laptop</option>
                        <option value="mac">Apple Mac / MacBook</option>
                        <option value="mobile">Mobile Devices Only (iOS/Android)</option>
                    </select>

                    <p>What data matters most to you? (Select all that apply)</p>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" name="data" value="financial"> Banking & Financial Records</label><br>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" name="data" value="photos"> Personal Photos & Memories</label><br>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" name="data" value="work"> Remote Work Documents & Client Data</label>
                </fieldset>
                <button type="button" class="cta-button">Next Step</button>
            </form>
        </main>

        <!-- Right Column: Contextual Sidebar Info (1fr) -->
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <h3>Why these questions matter</h3>
            <p>Different operating systems have entirely different vulnerability vectors. By indicating your primary devices, we prevent recommending unnecessary, bloated software packages.</p>
            
            <!-- Required Image 2: Illustrative User Type Icon Grid -->
            <div class="user-profiles-grid">
                <img src="images/user-profiles.png" alt="Icon grid illustrating target user types: The Remote Professional and The Small Shop Owner" class="sidebar-img">
            </div>
        </aside>
    </div>

    <!-- Consistent Site Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 CyberMatch. All rights reserved. | Protecting Your Digital Footprint.</p>
        <ul class="footer-links">
            <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="threat-index.html">Threat Level Index</a></li>
        </ul>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
